Title: The New Guy
Plot: After Myka leaves the warehouse, Pete gets a new partner: ATF agent Steven Jinks, who has a gift for sensing when someone is lying. Pete and Steven take on a new case in Denver, while Artie, Claudia, and Leena deal with a deadly pair of statues at Warehouse 13.
GuestStars: Aaron Ashmore, Ashley Williams, Jaime Murray, Mark Robinson
